### v02 — 2-Hand Flow (button rotate + SB/BB shift via /next-hand)
###
### S9 Cycle 6 Wave 3 신규 시나리오 (2026-05-12, issue #311).
### 본 시나리오는 v01 의 1-hand flow 위에 multi-hand state transition 을
### 검증한다. Hand 1 (v01 동일) → POST /api/session/:id/next-hand →
### Hand 2 setup 회전 (button +1, handNumber=2, state reset) 검증.
###
### 의존성:
###   - S8 Cycle 5 PR #301 (issue #287) — Engine harness POST /next-hand
###     endpoint + ManualNextHand event handler 머지 완료.
###     코드: team3-engine/lib/harness/server.dart (l.117 router, l.428 handler)
###     코드: team3-engine/lib/engine.dart (l.765 _handleManualNextHandFull)
###     테스트: team3-engine/test/harness/next_hand_endpoint_test.dart
###     스펙: docs/2. Development/2.3 Game Engine/Rules/Multi_Hand_State.md
###
### Pipeline (10 phase):
###   Phase A — Setup (health, variants, session 생성)
###   Phase B — Hand 1 preflop fold-to-BB (5 fold events)
###   Phase C — Hand 1 PotAward (BB idx 2 win)
###   Phase D — Hand 1 HandEnd (auto-rotate dealer 0->1, handNumber 0->1)
###   Phase E — Hand 1 final state 검증
###   Phase F — POST /next-hand (Hand 2 setup: dealer 1->2, handNumber 1->2) [KEY]
###   Phase G — Hand 2 rotation + state-reset 검증
###   Phase H — 2nd POST /next-hand (round-robin: dealer 2->3, handNumber 2->3)
###   Phase I — Round-robin 후 상태 검증 (folded->active 재설정 포함)
###   Phase J — Final session integrity (handNumber=3, dealer=3, 6 active seats)
###
### Coverage:
###   - Cycle 5 issue #287 (multi-hand state) 회귀 보장
###   - hand_end 자동 회전 + /next-hand 명시 회전 동시 검증
###   - state reset: community=[], currentBet=0, status folded->active
###   - sbSeat/bbSeat 위치 변화 (toJson 비노출 — 위치 계산으로 검증)
###
### 실행 검증: 2026-05-12 S9 Cycle 6 — Engine harness :18080 직결.
### Evidence: integration-tests/evidence/cycle6-2026-05-12/v02-2-hand-flow/

@engine = http://localhost:18080

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase A: Setup — Engine session 생성 (v01 동일 패턴)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### A.1 GET /health — Engine 가동 확인
GET {{engine}}/health

### A.2 GET /api/variants — 지원 variant 확인
GET {{engine}}/api/variants

### A.3 POST /api/session — NL Holdem 6-handed 세션 생성
# @name newSession
POST {{engine}}/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant": "nlh",
  "seats": 6
}

# Assertion (Phase A):
#   - sessionId matches /^[a-z0-9]+$/
#   - street === preflop
#   - dealerSeat === 0
#   - handNumber === 0
#   - seats[0].isDealer === true
#   - pot.main === 15

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase B: Hand 1 preflop — fold to BB (v01 동일)
# Dealer button on seat 1 (idx 0). 6-handed action order:
#   UTG (idx 3) -> idx 4 -> idx 5 -> dealer (idx 0) -> SB (idx 1) -> BB (idx 2) winner
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### B.1 POST event — Seat 4 (UTG, idx 3) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 3
}

### B.2 POST event — Seat 5 (idx 4) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 4
}

### B.3 POST event — Seat 6 (idx 5) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 5
}

### B.4 POST event — Seat 1 (dealer, idx 0) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 0
}

### B.5 POST event — Seat 2 (SB, idx 1) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 1
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase C: Hand 1 Pot Award
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### C.1 POST event — pot_awarded to BB (idx 2)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "pot_awarded",
  "awards": {
    "2": 15
  }
}

# Assertion:
#   - pot.main === 0
#   - seats[2].stack === 1005 (1000 - BB 10 + pot 15)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase D: Hand 1 HandEnd (Engine 자동 dealer 회전)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### D.1 POST event — hand_end
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "hand_end"
}

# Assertion (Engine §_endHandFull l.682-704):
#   - handNumber === 1 (0 -> 1, hand_end 자동 증가)
#   - dealerSeat === 1 (0 -> 1, hand_end 자동 회전 +1)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase E: Hand 1 final state 검증
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### E.1 GET /api/session/{id} — Hand 1 종료 상태 회수
GET {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 1, dealerSeat === 1
#   - pot.main === 0
#   - 1 active seat (winner BB idx 2), 5 folded
#   - seats[2].stack === 1005 (winner)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase F: POST /next-hand (Hand 2 setup) — KEY ENDPOINT 검증
#
# /next-hand 는 Cycle 5 issue #287 신규 추가. Triggers:
#   - dealerSeat += 1 -> 1 -> 2
#   - sbSeat / bbSeat 재계산
#   - handNumber += 1 -> 1 -> 2
#   - street -> idle, actionOn -> -1
#   - per-seat reset: holeCards=[], currentBet=0
#   - isDealer flag 갱신
#   - folded -> active 복귀 (Engine l.820-822)
#   - pot.main=0
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### F.1 POST /next-hand — Hand 2 회전 트리거 (KEY)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion (Engine §_handleManualNextHandFull l.765-830):
#   - handNumber === 2 (1 -> 2)
#   - dealerSeat === 2 (1 -> 2, +1 회전)
#   - seats[2].isDealer === true, others false
#   - seats[i].currentBet === 0 for all i
#   - seats[i].status === active for all i
#   - pot.main === 0

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase G: Hand 2 dealer 회전 + state reset 검증
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### G.1 GET /api/session/{id} — Hand 2 setup 결과 검증
GET {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}

# Assertion (Phase G):
#   - handNumber === 2, dealerSeat === 2
#   - seats[2].isDealer === true (others false)
#   - community === []
#   - all seats[].currentBet === 0
#   - all 6 seats status === active
#
# SB/BB 위치 (toJson 비노출 — 위치 계산):
#   - Hand 1 (dealer=0): SB=1, BB=2
#   - Hand 2 (dealer=2): SB=3, BB=4
#   - SB shift +2, BB shift +2, dealer +1 (사용자 spec 일치)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase H: 2nd /next-hand — round-robin 성질 검증
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### H.1 POST /next-hand — 2nd 회전 (Hand 3 setup)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 3 (2 -> 3)
#   - dealerSeat === 3 (2 -> 3, +1 회전)
#   - seats[3].isDealer === true, others false

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase I: Round-robin 후 상태 검증 + folded->active 복귀 재확인
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### I.1 GET /api/session/{id} — 2nd 회전 결과 검증
GET {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 3, dealerSeat === 3
#   - seats[3].isDealer === true
#   - 5 dealer-not seats: isDealer === false
#   - 모든 seat status === active
#   - community === [], 모든 seats[].currentBet === 0

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase J: Final session integrity (DoD 종합 검증)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### J.1 GET /api/session/{id} — 최종 누적 상태
GET {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}

# DoD Assertion (cumulative):
#   - sessionId 동일
#   - handNumber === 3 (Hand 1 hand_end + /next-hand × 2 = 3 증가)
#   - dealerSeat === 3 (0 -> 1 -> 2 -> 3)
#   - 6 seats 모두 active 상태
#   - 모든 stack 보존 (winner seat[2].stack === 1005, others 1000 or 995)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
